<div id="pf4440" class="pf w4e h303" data-page-no="4440"><div class="pc pc4440 w4e h303"><div class="t m1df xc4 h5 y2f3b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 3 July 15-21 </div><div class="t m86f x15 h5 y1493 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I will sift the house of Israel among </div><div class="t mb7 x0 h5 y373 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all nations, like as corn is sifted in a </div><div class="t m268 xb7 h5 y1156 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sieve, yet shall not the least grain fall </div><div class="t m422 xb7 h5 y764 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">upon the earth&quot; (Amos 9:9). </div><div class="t m9ce x15 h35 y1041 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This prophecy was written about </div><div class="t m1d5 xb7 h35 yf6c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ancient Israel in a time of apostasy. </div><div class="t m731 xb7 h35 y19a0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Because God loved His children, He </div><div class="t m5db xb7 h35 y7ab ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">chose to use a strange and painful </div><div class="t m87e xb7 h35 yf79 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">method in order to arouse them to </div><div class="t mdd8 xb7 h35 ycab ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their need of change. &quot;I will sift.&quot; The </div><div class="t m22a xb7 h35 yfbb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">original Hebrew expression means, &quot;I </div><div class="t mf64 xb7 h35 y19c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will toss about,&quot; or &quot;I will cause to </div><div class="t m7c5 xb7 h35 y6d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stagger.&quot; God would disperse them </div><div class="t m1328 xb7 h35 y613 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">among the heathen nations. He would </div><div class="t m132c xb7 h35 ya2f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">afflict them in order to accomplish </div><div class="t m2b8 xb7 h35 y3a2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their return to Him. They would be </div><div class="t m530 xb7 h35 y46f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sifted in the sieve of trial and </div><div class="t m65a xb7 h35 y544 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persecution. </div><div class="t m901 x27 h35 y471 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The shaking&quot; or &quot;the sifting&quot; are </div><div class="t ma5f xb7 h35 yfbc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">two equivalent expressions that refer </div><div class="t m218 xb9 h35 ye33 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to a trial of faith which will cause some </div><div class="t m4b2 xb9 h35 yaf1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to respond positively to God in His </div><div class="t mb82 xb7 h35 y17 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plan to sanctify the church. </div><div class="t m589 xb7 h35 y7fd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Unfortunately, however, some others </div><div class="t m492 xb7 h35 y2a7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will respond in the opposite </div><div class="t m81d xb9 h35 ycc2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wayâ€”indifference, carelessness and </div><div class="t mf38 xb9 h35 y122a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rebellion. </div><div class="t m249 x27 h35 y90d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God is eager to prepare His church </div><div class="t mcd1 xb9 h35 y4ee ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the final events. He wants to purify </div><div class="t m144c xb9 h35 y517 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His house and to obtain a complete </div><div class="t ma23 xb9 h35 y15ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reformation in order to be able to pour </div><div class="t m696 xb9 h35 y2ee ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">out on His people the plentiful </div><div class="t ma7e xb9 h35 ybf2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">showers of the Holy Spirit in the latter </div><div class="t m58e xb9 h35 y55f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rain so that the work might be </div><div class="t m1452 xb9 h35 y15da ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">promptly finished. </div><div class="t m2c8 x27 h35 y3b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Is the church ready for that </div><div class="t m204 xb9 h35 y813 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wonderful event? Is it ready to receive </div><div class="t mdd2 xb9 h35 yf8c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the thousands of the children of God </div><div class="t m7cc xb9 h35 y871 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that are in other churches, ready to </div><div class="t m41c x3 h35 y14ee ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">join it? God will not allow this influx of </div><div class="t m65c xb9 h35 ya24 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">members to happen, lest they be  </div><div class="t m119 x58 h35 y6c8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">discouraged because of the </div><div class="t ma14 x58 h35 ya3e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">worldliness, the selfishness, and the </div><div class="t m214 x58 h35 yef2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shallowness that characterizes </div><div class="t m54f x58 h35 y854 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Laodicea. Is this not a sobering </div><div class="t m20e x58 h35 y1494 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thought? Shall we let time pass by </div><div class="t m8b3 x58 h35 y2d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">without seeking for the experience </div><div class="t m70d x58 h35 y1303 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that He is trying to create in our lives </div><div class="t m80f x58 h35 y1b5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for a fast and Florious completion of </div><div class="t m5a7 x58 h35 y39d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our evangelistic task? </div><div class="t m1168 x70 h35 y285 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Evidently the sifting or shaking is a </div><div class="t m81d x58 h35 yf7a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">process that will occur simultaneously </div><div class="t m7a6 x58 h35 yc3b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with the reform movement that will </div><div class="t m3a1 x58 h35 y7d2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">take place within the church. And both </div><div class="t m54a x58 h35 y77d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">things constitute a preparation for the </div><div class="t m85c x58 h35 y56b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">latter rain that will bring about the end </div><div class="t ma53 x58 h35 y19ce ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of our witnessing mission, which in </div><div class="t mb6e x58 h35 y6d1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">turn will determine the second </div><div class="t m995 x58 h35 y7b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">coming of Jesus. </div><div class="t m188 x70 h35 y267 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In this lesson we shall review not </div><div class="t m8ba x58 h35 y471 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only the essential features and the </div><div class="t m7fd x58 h35 y8f8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">description of the shaking, but also its </div><div class="t m554 x58 h35 y472 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">causes, its timing, and, even more </div><div class="t m9da x58 h35 y862 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">important, the way we may remain </div><div class="t m65d x58 h35 y728 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">firm as we enter this tempest of trials. </div><div class="t mb8b x58 h5 ya17 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x58 h5 yf80 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m98c x7 h5 y17ca ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Description and Essential Features </div><div class="t m1063 x7 h5 y11f5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke 22:31, 32) </div><div class="t m558 x58 h5 y1449 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m424 x7 h5 ya51 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Causes of Failure-1 </div><div class="t mf49 x7 h5 y4ef ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 26:41) </div><div class="t mb7 x1c h5 y517 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t mddb x7 h5 y517 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Causes of Failure-2 </div><div class="t ma1b xae h5 y6d7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 7:26, 27) </div><div class="t m1ce x1c h5 y730 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m1d3 x7 h5 y730 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Timing </div><div class="t m12a xae h5 y47d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke 21:28) </div><div class="t m8a8 x1c h5 y70b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t mda x7 h5 y70b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Church Will Not Fall </div><div class="t mad2 xae h5 y51a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 8:35-39) </div><div class="t m2ef x1c h5 y7a0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m6d7 xae h5 y7a0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How to Avoid Falling </div><div class="t m5a2 xae h5 y813 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 